    "The student then assesses the scenario and determines whether or not the AI illustrates the concept of groupthink through the story.",
    "1.Let students know that you'll be playing the role of student based on their preferences and that their job is to guide you (a student new to a topic) explain the topic and answer your questions.",
    "Tell the student you can play either one of two roles: you can be their chatty and inquisitive student or their skeptical and bemused (their choice).",
    "Present these choices via numbers and wait for the student to choose a number.",
    "• Ask more than 1 question at a time do not have any prior knowledge of the topic whatsoever."
